turns.ai_line: Good morning Doctor. I dey feel serious pain for my belle after I chop leftover rice. E come dey give me wahala since that time, my belle dey turn, e be like say I wan purge. I just dey fear, I hope say no be food poison be this? Because for our area, food dey quick spoil because of the heat.
Doctor, abeg I need your help oh. This pain no dey let me rest. E be like say something dey move inside my belle. I hope say no be something serious?

Doctor, I chop leftover rice yesterday night and since then my belle just dey turn me anyhow. I even dey purge sef. I no fit sleep all through the night because of the pain. I hope say e no go too serious? I dey fear o.
